# 0.7.0 alpha
- Application->error now takes an Exception
- Application->error is now the default error handler
- Backend menu is now loaded from database
- Added ApplicationException
- Added FileHelper::uncompress
- Extensions in .tar.gz format are now supported
- Implemented update functionality
- Added ContentManager->gArticles, ContentManager->gCategories,
	CommentManager->gComments, MenuManager->gMenus,
	MenuManager->gMenuItems, UserManager->gUsers,
	UserManager->gUserGroups
- Replaced ModuleManager and PluginManager with ExtensionManager,
	now included in core
- Added ExtensionManager->gModules
- Added ExtensionManager->gPlugins

# 0.6.1 alpha
- Bug fixes

# 0.6.0 alpha
- Unpublished content is now only accessible to users with permission to
	VIEW_UNPUBLISHED
- Added UserPermissions::VIEW_UNPUBLISHED
- Added "View article|category page" link in content editors
- Categories now have pagination
- Bug fixes

